07:36.660 --> 07:42.380
strong incentives for the world's industries to transition. We can enforce strict standards for

07:42.380 --> 07:48.100
energy efficiency and for any type of new construction. We can phase out fossil fuel

07:48.100 --> 07:55.780
vehicles. Next, we also need to invent new and better technology. Without new technologies and

07:55.780 --> 08:01.420
innovation, it will be impossible to achieve a zero CO2 emission world, be it from technologies

